# Delegated Effects

This template declares permission `{{permission}}`.

- `read_only` actions must not delegate to effectful facades.
- `memory_write` actions may call only
  `AllbertAssist.DynamicPlugins.Delegate.run("append_memory", params, context)`.
- `external_network` actions may call only
  `AllbertAssist.DynamicPlugins.Delegate.run("external_network_request", params, context)`.

The trusted validator checks the literal facade name, action permission,
execution mode, exposure, and response metadata before the v0.37 loader can
compile a templated action into the core node.
